---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Regulatory Compliance"
  description="Weyland-Yutani Corporation maintains rigorous compliance across Earth-based and off-world regulatory frameworks, safety certifications, anti-corruption policies, and environmental standards."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[50vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center py-20">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
          <div class="h-px w-16 bg-[#FFC600]"></div>
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-mono">LEGAL & GOVERNANCE</span>
          <div class="h-px w-16 bg-[#FFC600]"></div>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-black text-white leading-none uppercase mb-6">
          REGULATORY <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">COMPLIANCE</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-48 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-8"></div>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wider font-mono leading-relaxed">
          OPERATING WITH INTEGRITY ACROSS EVERY JURISDICTION, EVERY WORLD
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 hazard-stripes h-2"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- OVERVIEW -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-5"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">COMPLIANCE FRAMEWORK</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-8 uppercase">PRINCIPLED OPERATIONS AT INTERSTELLAR SCALE</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Weyland-Yutani Corporation operates within a complex regulatory environment that spans 47 terrestrial nations, multiple intergovernmental bodies, and the Interstellar Commerce Commission's off-world governance framework. The Corporation maintains a dedicated Global Compliance Division staffed by more than 2,000 legal, regulatory, and compliance professionals responsible for ensuring full adherence to all applicable laws, regulations, and industry standards.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our compliance program is built on four pillars: prevention through policy and training, detection through monitoring and audit, response through investigation and remediation, and continuous improvement through feedback and adaptation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EARTH-BASED REGULATIONS -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">TERRESTRIAL COMPLIANCE</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-8 uppercase">EARTH-BASED REGULATORY FRAMEWORK</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-base font-black text-white uppercase mb-2">SECURITIES AND FINANCIAL REGULATION</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Full compliance with U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) reporting requirements, Sarbanes-Oxley Act provisions, Japan Financial Services Agency regulations, European Securities and Markets Authority directives, and all applicable stock exchange listing standards.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-base font-black text-white uppercase mb-2">DATA PROTECTION AND PRIVACY</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Compliance with the European Union General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), Japan's Act on Protection of Personal Information (APPI), and equivalent data protection legislation across all operating jurisdictions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-base font-black text-white uppercase mb-2">ENVIRONMENTAL REGULATION</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Adherence to all applicable environmental legislation, including the U.S. Clean Air Act, EU Environmental Liability Directive, and international agreements governing industrial emissions, waste disposal, and resource extraction on Earth.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-base font-black text-white uppercase mb-2">EXPORT CONTROLS AND TRADE COMPLIANCE</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Compliance with International Traffic in Arms Regulations (ITAR), Export Administration Regulations (EAR), EU Dual-Use Regulation, and all applicable trade sanctions programs. The Corporation maintains a dedicated export compliance team and automated screening systems.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-base font-black text-white uppercase mb-2">LABOR AND EMPLOYMENT LAW</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Full compliance with all applicable labor laws, including wage and hour regulations, workplace safety standards (OSHA, EU Framework Directive 89/391), anti-discrimination laws, and collective bargaining agreements across all Earth-based operations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- OFF-WORLD REGULATIONS -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-black">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">OFF-WORLD COMPLIANCE</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-8 uppercase">INTERSTELLAR REGULATORY BODIES</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-base font-black text-white uppercase mb-2">INTERSTELLAR COMMERCE COMMISSION (ICC)</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">The ICC is the primary regulatory authority for commercial operations beyond Earth orbit. Weyland-Yutani maintains ICC Class A operator certification, the highest classification available, and complies with all ICC directives governing colony administration, interstellar commerce, vessel operations, and off-world labor standards.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-base font-black text-white uppercase mb-2">UNITED NATIONS COMMITTEE ON EXTRATERRESTRIAL SETTLEMENT (UNCES)</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Compliance with UNCES directives governing terraforming operations, atmospheric processing standards, colony habitability certification, and the rights of off-world residents.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-base font-black text-white uppercase mb-2">COLONIAL ADMINISTRATION AUTHORITY</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Adherence to CAA regulations governing colony governance structures, resident safety standards, emergency response protocols, and the provision of essential services to colony populations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SAFETY CERTIFICATIONS -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">CERTIFICATIONS</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-8 uppercase">SAFETY AND QUALITY CERTIFICATIONS</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="p-6 bg-black border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs font-bold">ISO 9001:2115</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Quality Management Systems</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-black border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs font-bold">ISO 14001:2115</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Environmental Management Systems</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-black border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs font-bold">ISO 45001:2118</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Occupational Health & Safety</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-black border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs font-bold">ICC-SA CERT. CLASS A</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Interstellar Operator Certification</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-black border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs font-bold">ITSB LEVEL 5</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">International Terraforming Standards Board</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-black border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs font-bold">NSF SYNTHETIC CLEARANCE</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">National Science Foundation, Synthetic Persons</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ANTI-CORRUPTION & WHISTLEBLOWER -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-black">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
            <div>
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">INTEGRITY</span>
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-6 uppercase">ANTI-CORRUPTION POLICY</h2>
              <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                  Weyland-Yutani maintains a zero-tolerance policy toward bribery, corruption, and improper payments in all forms. The Corporation's Anti-Corruption Policy prohibits all employees, officers, directors, agents, and third-party representatives from offering, paying, soliciting, or accepting bribes or corrupt payments in any jurisdiction.
                </p>
                <p>
                  The Corporation complies with the U.S. Foreign Corrupt Practices Act (FCPA), the UK Bribery Act, Japan's Unfair Competition Prevention Act, and all equivalent anti-corruption legislation. All employees receive annual anti-corruption training, and high-risk operations are subject to enhanced due diligence and monitoring.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Third-party agents and contractors are subject to pre-engagement due diligence screening and are contractually obligated to comply with the Corporation's Anti-Corruption Policy.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">REPORTING</span>
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-6 uppercase">WHISTLEBLOWER PROTECTION</h2>
              <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                  The Corporation is committed to maintaining an environment in which employees and other stakeholders can report concerns about suspected violations of law, regulation, or Corporation policy without fear of retaliation.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Reports may be made through the following channels:
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 ml-4">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#FFC600] mt-0.5 text-xs">&#9632;</span> The Corporation's confidential Ethics Hotline, available 24/7 across all jurisdictions</li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#FFC600] mt-0.5 text-xs">&#9632;</span> Direct report to the Chief Compliance Officer</li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#FFC600] mt-0.5 text-xs">&#9632;</span> The secure online reporting portal at ethics.weylandyutani.com</li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#FFC600] mt-0.5 text-xs">&#9632;</span> Anonymous submission via encrypted relay</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                  Retaliation against individuals who report concerns in good faith is strictly prohibited and will result in disciplinary action up to and including termination of employment.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ENVIRONMENTAL COMPLIANCE -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-mono">ENVIRONMENTAL RESPONSIBILITY</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-8 uppercase">TERRAFORMING AND ENVIRONMENTAL COMPLIANCE</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              As the galaxy's leading terraforming operator, Weyland-Yutani holds a unique responsibility to ensure that atmospheric processing and planetary modification activities are conducted with the highest environmental standards. The Corporation's terraforming operations comply with the UNCES Planetary Modification Code, the ITSB Operating Standards, and all applicable environmental impact assessment requirements.
            </p>
            <p>
              All terraforming projects undergo comprehensive environmental impact assessment before initiation, including evaluation of existing planetary ecosystems (where present), atmospheric modeling, hydrological impact analysis, and long-term climate projection. The Corporation does not initiate terraforming operations on worlds with confirmed indigenous biospheres without UNCES authorization.
            </p>
            <p>
              On Earth, the Corporation's manufacturing and research operations maintain full compliance with all applicable environmental regulations, including emissions standards, waste management requirements, and water quality standards. The Corporation publishes an annual Environmental Performance Report, audited by independent third parties, detailing emissions, resource consumption, and environmental remediation activities.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="/sustainability" class="btn-primary px-8 py-3 text-sm inline-block text-center">SUSTAINABILITY REPORT</a>
            <a href="/governance/ethics" class="btn-secondary px-8 py-3 text-sm inline-block text-center">ETHICS & COMPLIANCE</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
